org.ingatan.data
Class HistoryEntry

java.lang.Object
  org.ingatan.data.HistoryEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<HistoryEntry>
public class HistoryEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<HistoryEntry>

A quiz results history. The Library class encapsulates an ArrayList of these to represent the history of times that the library was used, and what the grade was. This is where the statistics centre gets the data from to produce the graphs.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Thomas Everingham

Parameters:

questionsAnswered - Number of questions answered by the user in that particular quiz.
grade - The average grade the user received over all questions answered.
averageImprovement - Average improvement on the average of previous attempts at the questions.
